  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a xcb-util-keysyms</title>

    <para>
      The <application>xcb-util-keysyms</application> package contains a library
for handling standard X key constants and conversion to/from keycodes.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

