    <title>Instalao de xcb-util-keysyms</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>xcb-util-keysyms</application> executando os seguintes
comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure $XORG_CONFIG &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      <!--To test the results, issue:
